_Intro-0:
Long ago, two races
lived in harmony and ruled
the world: Humans and Monsters.
_Intro-1:
But one day, humans believed
a monster attempted to seize
a human soul.
_Intro-2:
Later, the humans' princess,
Razberry, vanished.
_Intro-3:
The human queen was enraged.
She forced the king
to wage war...
_Intro-4:
In the end, humans
emerged victorious.
_Intro-5:
Monsters were sealed
beneath the ocean.
_Intro-6:
They say all who ventured
too close to the cliff...
Disappeared...
_NameInit-4:
Now you bear responsibility
for Frida...
_NameInit-9:
She's the last hope
for the monsters...
_NameInit-10: Are you ready for this duty?
_NameInit-13:
Welp. Return when
you are prepared...
_NameInit-17:
Go now. Bring hope for
a happy ending to all beings...
